everything that you need!

44:35.805 --> 44:37.040
Okay, that's not true.

44:37.073 --> 44:39.742
"Oh, honey,
isn't this place great?

44:39.776 --> 44:41.611
Don't you think he's nice?

44:41.644 --> 44:43.780
