fucking adventure?

45:09.106 --> 45:10.273
I'm sorry, okay?

45:10.307 --> 45:11.675
You're right.

45:11.708 --> 45:13.610
You're totally right.

45:13.643 --> 45:15.879
[sighs]
I'm sorry, Henry.

45:16.746 --> 45:19.016
