for a free place to stay?

46:49.306 --> 46:50.507
Excuse me?

46:50.540 --> 46:52.909
Thomas is the only nice guy
that you have ever been with,

46:52.942 --> 46:54.477
and you fucked that up too.

46:54.511 --> 46:55.679
Want to know what I think?

46:55.712 --> 46:58.048
I think you're just
a fucking sad,

46:58.081 --> 47:00.751
